Jaws/Punch:





Jaws chased after a fish, catching up to it and bring his teeth down upon it, 
tearing it apart and then devouring.  That was good, he thought, heading back 
towards the Alliance Island, no longer hungry and he had a revived energy 
supply.

---

Punch sighed, scanning the site of the Chivtron/Maximal/Chosen 
Mafia/Radicon/NDE battle, wishing he could take part.  But Zardus was gone on 
another one of his adventures.  He sighed again, slamming a fist and cursing, 
tired of monitoring the slagging bridge.
